\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
Note that for any 
\begin_inset Formula $v,w\in V$
\end_inset

, our function 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{v,w}$
\end_inset

 is the composition of continous functions and thus the result follows.
\begin_inset Foot
status open

